---
// Editorial colophon for Featured Research pages.
// Self-contained: outer wrapper aligns to the same horizontal column as the article body
// (max-w-3xl + px-6) so it matches the body left edge when placed below RelatedResearch.
// Inner text column is narrower (max-w-xl) for an inset footnote feel.
// Do not add: avatars, backgrounds, badges, "About" headers, icons, or container styling.
// The premium feeling comes from restraint, not added elements.
---

<section class="bg-white pb-16 md:pb-20">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="border-t border-[#0A0F1E]/12 pt-6 mt-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl space-y-3">
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-7 text-body">
          Ranking Atlas is a specialist data campaigns firm. We turn proprietary data, commissioned research, and original analysis into stories and studies that earn authoritative coverage.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-6">
          For methodology questions, additional data cuts, or research enquiries: <a href="mailto:contact@ranking-atlas.com" class="text-brand hover:underline">contact@ranking-atlas.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
